\par 
\par When the Attorney-General ceased, a buzz arose in the court as if
\par a cloud of great blue-flies were swarming about the prisoner, in
\par anticipation of what he was soon to become. When toned down again, the
\par unimpeachable patriot appeared in the witness-box.
\par 
\par Mr. Solicitor-General then, following his leader's lead, examined the
