\par 
\par Yet, this Mr. Carton took in more of the details of the scene than he
\par appeared to take in; for now, when Miss Manette's head dropped upon
\par her father's breast, he was the first to see it, and to say audibly:
\par "Officer! look to that young lady. Help the gentleman to take her out.
\par Don't you see she will fall!"
\par 
