\par him. "Oh, the men, the men!"
\par 
\par "But my dear!" began Defarge.
\par 
\par "But my dear!" repeated madame, nodding firmly; "but my dear! You are
\par faint of heart to-night, my dear!"
\par 
\par "Well, then," said Defarge, as if a thought were wrung out of his
\par breast, "it _is_ a long time."
\par 
