\par 
\par Then madame, with her teeth set, tied a very terrible knot indeed.
\par 
\par "Hold!" cried Defarge, reddening a little as if he felt charged with
\par cowardice; "I too, my dear, will stop at nothing."
\par 
\par "Yes! But it is your weakness that you sometimes need to see your victim
