\par 
\par "'There is another patient.'
\par 
\par "I was startled, and asked, 'Is it a pressing case?'
\par 
\par "'You had better see,' he carelessly answered; and took up a light.
\par 
\par         *****
\par 
\par "The other patient lay in a back room across a second staircase, which
\par was a species of loft over a stable. There was a low plastered ceiling
\par to a part of it; the rest was open, to the ridge of the tiled roof, and
